cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image registration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning for similarity metric learning (Learning Deep Similarity Metric) suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of 3D images and medical imaging techniques may also suggest the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
